In MSTest v4, `Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>` returns the typed value directly instead of using an `out` parameter. Here's the fix:

```csharp
// Before: Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>(obj, out var typed);
// After:  var typed = Assert.IsInstanceOfType<T>(obj);
```

